  This happens with this variant:
  ```yaml
  - batch: 16
    in_channels: 128
    in_height: 8
    in_width: 8
    out_channels: 64
    kernel_height: 128  # This is wrong - kernel_height=128 is much larger than input height=8!
    kernel_width: 2
    stride: 2
    padding: 2
